<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>My Pretty Baby</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<div id="desktop">

<div id="sticker1">★</div>
<div id="sticker2">:)</div>
<div id="sticker3">CD</div>

<div class="icon" onclick="openWindow('computer')">
<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3474/3474360.png">
<span>My Computer</span>
</div>

<div class="icon" onclick="openWindow('documents')">
<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/716/716784.png">
<span>Documents</span>
</div>

<div class="icon" onclick="openWindow('photos')">
<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1375/1375106.png">
<span>Photos</span>
</div>

<div class="icon" onclick="openWindow('music')">
<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3659/3659784.png">
<span>Music</span>
</div>

<div class="icon" onclick="openWindow('messenger')">
<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/9068/9068756.png">
<span>Messenger</span>
</div>

<div class="icon" onclick="openWindow('terminal')">
<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1792/1792899.png">
<span>Terminal</span>
</div>

</div>

<div class="window" id="computer">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>My Computer</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('computer')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">
<h3>System Information</h3>

<p>Computer Name: MY PRETTY BABY</p>
<p>Operating System: Y2K Edition</p>
<p>RAM: 1024 MB</p>
<p>Most Active Process:</p>

<pre>thinking_about_user.exe</pre>

<button onclick="openWindow('system32')">
Open system32
</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="window" id="documents">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>Documents</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('documents')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">

<h3>Files</h3>

<div class="file" onclick="openNote('note1')">
readme.txt
</div>

<div class="file" onclick="openNote('note2')">
diagnostics.txt
</div>

<div class="file" onclick="openNote('note3')">
system_log.txt
</div>

</div>
</div>

<div class="window" id="photos">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>Photos</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('photos')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">

<h3>Photos</h3>

<img class="photo" src="assets/photo1.jpg">
<img class="photo" src="assets/photo2.jpg">
<img class="photo" src="assets/photo3.jpg">

<p>
Replace these with your own photos.
</p>

</div>
</div>

<div class="window" id="music">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>Music</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('music')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">

<h3>Playlist</h3>

<p>
Put your music website link below:
</p>

<a href="#" target="_blank">
Open Playlist
</a>

</div>
</div>

<div class="window" id="messenger">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>Messenger</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('messenger')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">

<h3>Friends Online</h3>

<div class="contact">
Trisha
<br>
Status: Online
</div>

</div>
</div>

<div class="window" id="terminal">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>Terminal</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('terminal')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">

<pre id="terminalOutput">
Type help below.
</pre>

<input
id="terminalInput"
placeholder="command..."
onkeydown="terminalCommand(event)"
>

</div>
</div>

<div class="window" id="system32">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>system32</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('system32')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">

<h3>Access Restricted</h3>

<input
type="password"
id="passwordBox"
placeholder="Password"
>

<button onclick="checkPassword()">
Unlock
</button>

<p id="passwordMessage"></p>

</div>
</div>

<div class="window" id="secret">
<div class="titlebar">
<span>final_message.txt</span>
<button onclick="closeWindow('secret')">✕</button>
</div>

<div class="content">

<h2>Hey.</h2>

<p>
If you've reached this folder,
you explored everything.

I knew you would.

Thank you for every conversation,
every joke,
every memory.

You're important to me.

♡
</p>

</div>
</div>

<div id="taskbar">

<button id="startButton">
Start
</button>

<div id="clock"></div>

</div>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
